tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
  response_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  survey_id UUID NOT NULL,
  respondent_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  response_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  question1 TEXT,
  question2 TEXT,
  question3 TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE SurveyResponses (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  respondent_id INT,
  survey_id INT,
  response_date TIMESTAMP,
  response_text TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE SurveyQuestions (
  question_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  survey_id INT,
  question_text TEXT,
  question_type VARCHAR(50),
  is_required BOOL
);

CREATE TABLE SurveyResponse (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  respondent_name VARCHAR(50),
  response_text TEXT,
  survey_id INT,
  response_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE SurveyQuestion (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  question_text TEXT,
  question_type VARCHAR(20),
  survey_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE Survey (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  survey_name VARCHAR(100),
  creation_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE Feedback (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  respondent_name VARCHAR(50),
  feedback_text TEXT,
  feedback_date DATE,
  survey_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    respondent_id INT,
    survey_id INT,
    question_id INT,
    response TEXT
);
